<table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td>
	     <table class=mform  border=0 cellpadding=1 cellspacing=0 width=100%>
	     <form action=/cgi-bin/mrate.pl name=f106183706825077>
	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=>Check List</a> <a id=fs8 href=#post><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11"></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Mon, Aug 25th 2:56 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=/db/poster.html?user=136367><span id= >ShadoKera</span></a><br><span id=notbold>2 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Have a friend working on this. I took some time to go through all the threads for each of the steps for this quest. I've compiled a check list for easier reference. All the information in this post is a complied list from other posters. Hope you find it useful!<br><br>Part one: Willamina's Needles <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2183" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2183</a><br><br>( ) The History of Evils: The Age of Scale <br>Loc: n100 p1000, pos68 (so you know which floor) <br>next to Sir Geravaldi&nbsp;&nbsp;on the left side of library. Bottom shelf of book case. Looks like very small book. Spawns every 5-30 minutes. <br><br>( ) Take book to Agrakth Theric <br>Loc: n553 p1207 Robed Erudite in Evil part of town on a hill near the wall. <br><br>( ) Take the item he gives you to Caden Zharik <br>Loc: n341 p744 Gnome in the inner ring <br><br>( ) Take the standard to Boiron Ston <br>Loc: p34 p331 merchant Dwarf in the inner ring <br><br>( ) Take the note to Elisha Dirtyshoes <br>Loc: p394 p938 Human in a &quot;wooden&quot; room in the inner ring <br><br>( ) Take the ring to Arch Mage Narik <br>Loc: p418 p22 Robed Human in the neutral part of town (in the caster guild I think) <br><br>( ) Take the jewel to Onirelin Gali <br>Loc: n643 p1043 Dark Elf in the evil part of town <br><br>( ) Take the Artifact to Oracle Cador <br>Loc: p622 p110 Barbarian located in the good part of town near PoT zone <br><br>( ) Take the Black Lava Powder to Mirao Frostpouch <br>Loc: n89 n208 Barbarian located on the neutral part of town (in shammy guild I think) <br><br>( ) Take the Curing Elixer to Bolcen Tendag <br>Loc: p680 p949 Barbarian located in the good part of town in one of the staircases to an upper ramp. <br><br>( ) Take the Needles to Willamina <br>Loc n433 p1159 Halfling near the tree in the good part of town. <br><br>She gives you the Planar Traveller's Guide. <br>===========================================<br><br>Part Two: Beginner Magic Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2218" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2218</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Acomar Lothwol, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Pos 680, Pos 820 ground level<br><br>( ) Hand in the Hobgoblin surprise and your Planar Traveler's Manual to Acomar.<br><br>Bake a Hobgoblin Surprise or buy one in the bazaar for about 200pp<br><br>Hobgoblin Surprise<br>This is a Enduring Meal<br>DEX: +5   AGI: +5   <br>WT: 0.4   Size: MEDIUM<br>Class: NONE<br>Race: NONE<br><br>Components: brown gravy, hobgoblin meat, loaf of bread, pie tin<br>In: tanaan oven, collapsible spit<br>Yield: 1<br>Also Returns: pie tin<br>On Failure Returns: pie tin<br><br><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=149&amp;rsa=Baking&amp;sub=pop&amp;sb=item&amp;menustr=080020060000" target=_new>http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=149&amp;rsa=Baking&amp;sub=pop&amp;sb=item&amp;menustr=080020060000</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Three: Beginner Stealth Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2216" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2216</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Winon Glahar, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Neg 115,  Pos 60 ground level<br><br>( ) Make the stein (Planar Peridot Encrusted Stein) and hand in both stein and manual to receive your Beginner Stealth Manual.<br><br><br>Make a Planar Peridot Encrusted Stein (pottery) or buy one in the bazaar<br><br>Planar Peridot Encrusted Stein<br>MAGIC ITEM <br>Slot: PRIMARY,SECONDARY<br>AC: 3<br>CHA: +6   MANA: +15   <br>SV COLD: +15   <br>Required level of 10<br>WT: 0.6   Size: SMALL<br>Class: ALL<br>Race: ALL<br><br>Components: crystalline valor glaze, high quality firing sheet, lacquered peridot, unfired planar stein<br>In: kiln, tanaan kiln<br>Yield: 1<br><br>	unfired planar stein<br><br>	Components: block of tanaan clay, ceramic lining sketch, sculpting tools, tainted planar essence, water flask<br>	In: pottery wheel, tanaan pottery wheel<br>	Yield: 1<br>	Also Returns: sculpting tools<br>	On Failure Returns: sculpting tools<br><br><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/pottery_recipe_page.php?article=116&amp;rsa=Pottery&amp;sub=stein&amp;sb=item&amp;menustr=080090060000" target=_new>http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/pottery_recipe_page.php?article=116&amp;rsa=Pottery&amp;sub=stein&amp;sb=item&amp;menustr=080090060000</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Four: Beginner Combat Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2214" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2214</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Zauvudd Gigoth, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Neg 662, Pos 911  <br><br>( ) Hand in Planar Blood Brew and your Planar Traveler's Manual for your Beginner Combat Manual<br><br>Make or buy Planar Blood Brew (brewing) in the bazzar<br><br>Planar Blood Brew<br>This is a Miraculous Drink<br>STR: +3   STA: +3   CHA: -10   <br>SV DISEASE: +10   SV POISON: +10   <br>WT: 0.4   Size: SMALL<br>Class: ALL<br>Race: ALL<br><br>Components: bubonian blood, cask, cork, corking device, grapes, nightmare mephit blood, slarghilug blood, soda water<br>In: tanaan brew barrel<br>Yield: 1<br>Also Returns: corking device<br>On Failure Returns: corking device<br>Notes: used in a quest<br><br><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=36&amp;rsa=Brewing&amp;sb=item&amp;sub=non-alcoholic&amp;menustr=080030020000" target=_new>http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=36&amp;rsa=Brewing&amp;sb=item&amp;sub=non-alcoholic&amp;menustr=080030020000</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Five: Intermediate Magic Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2228" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2228</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Cadelid Etord, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Pos 665, Pos 811 <br><br>( ) Give him your Beginner Magic Manual and the Heart of Vhaksiz.<br><br>Heart of Vhaksiz drops off Vhaksiz the Shade in Plane of Nightmare<br><br>Level 65 Undead<br><br><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10238" target=_new>http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10238</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Six: Intermediate Stealth Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2238" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2238</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Leramas Feston, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Neg 114, Pos 74<br><br>( ) Turn in the head of Rallicus Rattican and your Beginners Stealth Manual to Leramas Feston and receive your Intermediate Stealth Manual.<br><br>Head of Rallicus Rattican drops off Rallicus Rattican in Plane of Disease<br><br>Level 61<br><a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10215" target=_new>http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=10215</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Seven: Intermediate Combat Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2226" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2226</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Xasri Virek, Quest NPC<br>Loc: unknown<br><br>( ) Xasri Virek requires that you prove your worth by killing the Junk Beast and returning his power source. Your reward is the Intermediate Combat Manual.<br><br>Junk Beast Power Source drops off the Junk Beast in Plane of Innovation<br><br>Level 60<br><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2226" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2226</a><br>===========================================<br><br>Part Eight: Advanced Magic Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2272" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2272</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Zalil Nyvin, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Pos 695 Pos 815<br><br>Hand in a <br>( ) Tornado Gem,<br>( ) a Battle Worn Trinket, <br>( ) and a Blue Diamond along with your Intermediate Magic Manual to Zalil Nyvin.<br><br>Tornado Gem is found in Bastion of Thunder and it drops off <br>A Vind Geistlig (Level: 62) <br>A Vind Militis (Level: 62) <br>A Vind Vill (Level: 61)<br><br>a Battle Worn Trinket is found in Drunder, Fortress of Zek<br>===========================================<br><br>Part Nine: Advanced Stealth Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2239" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2239</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Ethoach Trokith, Quest NPC<br>Loc: unknown<br><br>Hand in <br>( ) a Blizzard Gem, <br>( ) a Symbol of the Diaku, <br>( ) a Blue Diamond, and your Intermediate Stealth Manual to Ethoach Trokith<br><br>Blizzard Gem is found in Bastion of Thunder and it drops off<br>A Vann Geistlig (Levels: 62 - 63) <br>A Vann Hellig (Level: 63) <br>A Vann Kriger (Level: 64) <br>A Vann Militis (Levels: 62 - 63) <br><br>Symbol of the Diaku is found in both Drunder, Fortress of Zek and Plane of Storms<br>Drunder, Fortress of Zek<br>A Diaku Death Knight (Levels: 63 - 64) <br>A Diaku Oracle (Level: 63) <br>A Diaku Raider (Level: 60) <br>A Diaku Scout (Levels: 60 - 62) <br>A Diaku Warrior (Levels: 62 - 63) <br>Diaku Elite Armsman (Levels: 68 - 69) <br>Diaku Elite Guard (Level: 65) <br>Diaku Elite Sentry (Level: 68) <br>Diaku Sentry (Level: 60) <br>The Diaku Overseer (Level: 68) <br><br>Plane of Storms<br>A Diaku Raider (Level: 60) <br>===========================================<br><br>Part Ten: Advanced Combat Manual <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2227" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2227</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Gwiraba Gelrid, Quest NPC<br>Loc: unknown<br><br>Hand in <br>( ) a Sandstorm Gem,<br>( ) a Rage Filled Gem, <br>( ) and a Blue Diamond and your Intermediate Combat Manual to Gwiraba Gelrid<br><br><br>Sandstorm Gem is found in Bastion of Thunder and drops off<br>A Jord Kriger (Level: 64) <br>A Jord Militis (Level: 63) <br>A Jord Profet (Level: 62) <br>A Jord Tyv (Levels: 62 - 63) <br>Rorek Steelthorn (Level: 64) <br>Thorolf Sutherland (Level: 64) <br>Ymir Stormseer (Level: 64) <br><br>a Rage Filled Gem is found in Drunder, Fortress of Zek and drops off<br>Drunder, Fortress of Zek<br>Anival The Blade (Level: 68) <br>Hendin Shadow Master (Level: 68) <br>===========================================<br><br>FINAL STEP!!!!!!!<br><br>Three Manuals <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2273" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2273</a><br><br>Plane of Knowledge<br>Tenada Jeried, Quest NPC<br>Loc: Pos 17, Pos 46<br><br>( ) Advanced Combat Manual<br>( ) Advanced Magic Manual<br>( ) Advanced Stealth Manual<br>( ) Hope Stone<br><br>Hope Stone is found in Doomfire, The Burning Lands and drops off Fennin Ro<br> <br>Doomfire, The Burning Lands<br>Fennin Ro, The Tyrant of Fire (Level: 75) <br><br>Tenada asks you to give her all three advanced Manuals along with a hope stone, which drops rarely from mobs in the elemental planes.<br><br>GRATS!<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Aug 25 23:09:45 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
